events.title: Creed Fisher
events.location: Atlanta, Georgia, United States Of America
events.description: Main floor is general admission standing. Balcony is reserved seating. GA floor has a pit area with limited capacity. GA ticketholders who arrive after the pit is full will be directed to other open areas on the floor. Doors at 7:00 PM. Show at 8:00 PM. All ages welcome.
